     summary(drv, verbose = TRUE)
     (you should see a full description of the MySQLDriver object)
(2)  try other dbConnect methods, namely
      con <- dbConnect("MySQL")
      con <- dbConnect(MySQL())
(3) What do you see if you type
      getMethods("dbConnect")

Regards,

--
David

